summary: An Ordinance accepting a deed, dated the 16th day of June, 1911, from John A. McGonigle, a bachelor, to the North 30 feet of the following described real estate: Commencing 656.98 feet West of the Northeast corner of the L. M. Collins Donation Claim No. 46; thence South 398.24 feet; thence West 218.18 feet; thence North 398.24 feet; thence East 218.18 feet to point of beginning, containing 2 acres more or less, for street purposes only.
